Casting to \fIbool\fP results in \fBFalse\fP for all \fBNOOP\fP instances in the 
library (\fI\%NOOP_SEQ\fP, \fBNOOP_COLOR\fP and \fI\%NOOP_STYLE\fP). This is intended.
.UNINDENT
